  "compilation_error": "",
  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个send_notification的状态图，核心是描述从初始状态到最终ACCEPTED的完整流程。系统有两种入口：一种是有文件要上传的情况，另一种是没有文件直接发送。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "WAITING_FILE",
        "SENDING",
        "ACCEPTED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以起点会分出两条路径。我想确认一下：有文件的情况是先进入WAITING_FILE状态，然后再转到SENDING；没文件的话直接跳到SENDING对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "WAITING_FILE",
        "SENDING"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这个逻辑。WAITING_FILE到SENDING的触发条件我们标注为\"Presenza di file da caricare\"，另一条直接到SENDING的标注为\"No file\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WAITING_FILE",
        "SENDING"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把初始分支和这两个状态加进去了。接下来SENDING之后是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SENDING"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "SENDING之后进入REGISTERED状态，表示在SEND平台上创建了实体。然后这里又分叉：如果有文件要上传，就走到UPLOADED；如果没有文件，直接到COMPLETE。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SENDING",
        "REGISTERED",
        "UPLOADED",
        "COMPLETE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "REGISTERED到COMPLETE的标注我写\"No file da caricare\"，REGISTERED到UPLOADED写\"File caricati\"。然后UPLOADED之后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "REGISTERED",
        "UPLOADED",
        "COMPLETE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "UPLOADED直接到COMPLETE，然后COMPLETE再到ACCEPTED。最后ACCEPTED回到终点。注意ACCEPTED的标注要说明这是SEND平台返回的状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "UPLOADED",
        "COMPLETE",
        "ACCEPTED",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "全部完成了。我检查一下：起点分两支，经过WAITING_FILE或直达SENDING，再到REGISTERED，然后分有文件和无文件两条路到COMPLETE，最后到ACCEPTED结束。图标题用\"Stati send_notification\"可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "statediagram",
        "ACCEPTED",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题，这个状态流转准确反映了业务逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "statediagram"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
